  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Digital Marketing Intern",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work closely with the digital marketing and creative team to execute digital marketing strategies.</li>\n  <li>Researching topics, creating style guides for campaigns' content, and create content that helps drive conversions based on the campaign objectives.</li>\n  <li>Facilitate with the creative team during video shoots to ensure quality and alignment with client expectations.</li>\n  <li>Create high-quality and engaging relevant content for Facebook, Instagram, and TikTok.</li>\n  <li>Proactively contribute ideas in brainstorming sessions.</li>\n  <li>Create effective marketing copy to achieve social media campaign objectives.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Skills Required:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No prior experience required.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in written and verbal skills to effectively communication within the team.</li>\n  <li>Good organisation skills to coordinate and manage multiple priorities</li>\n  <li>Independent learner and team player</li>\n  <li>Good in content development, curation, and writing skill.</li>\n</ul>",
